knowledgeGraph.title: Texas Health Presbyterian Hospital Dallas
knowledgeGraph.description: Texas Health Presbyterian Hospital Dallas is a teaching hospital and tertiary care facility in the United States, located in the Vickery Meadow area of Dallas, Texas.

organic.title: Texas Health Dallas | Hospital in Dallas, TX
organic.snippet: Welcome to Texas Health Dallas. For more than a half-century, Texas Health Presbyterian Hospital Dallas has been at the forefront of health care in North Texas.

organic.title: Texas Health Resources | Health & Hospital System in North Texas
organic.snippet: With 24 hospitals around Dallas-Fort Worth, Texas Health Resources provides care in most North Texas communities. Call 1-877-THR-WELL for more information.

organic.title: Texas Health Presbyterian Hospital of Dallas
organic.snippet: Presbyterian Healthcare System is leading a generation of hospitals, designing new and better approaches for delivering the benefits of medicine.

organic.title: Texas Oncology-Presbyterian Cancer Center Dallas
organic.snippet: Our comprehensive cancer center is staffed with knowledgeable and supportive teams to tend to chemotherapy, radiation therapy, and other vital services.
